# Security headers for all responses (Cloudflare Workers Static Assets).
# Astro copies public/_headers → dist/_headers, which wrangler reads as the
# assets header rules. See https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/headers/
#
# Note: a Content-Security-Policy is intentionally omitted for now — a strict
# policy needs careful allow-listing (the CF Web Analytics beacon, inline
# bootstrap scripts, JSON-LD) and is tracked as a follow-up hardening item.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
